{
  "stem": "19807.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, very quickly to deviate from that, Victor Borge took it upon himself as a Dane to tell the whole world that the Danish people-- and they were wonderful, no question about it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Most of the Jews were saved over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were 7,000 Jews and I believe 5,000 of them were saved.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Fantastic, great.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But nobody knows-- very few people know throughout the world that 50,000 Jews in their entirety were saved in Bulgaria.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So my personal mission is to make sure that people begin to know about that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Life was beautiful there, it really was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We worked a half a day--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Well, it was like five hours and then three or three and a half hours we studied in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I love working with animals, so-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --that we would go and we'd work in the fields.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We would harvest, we would sow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We would harvest potatoes, we would harvest [INAUDIBLE], which was called.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was the food that we would get for the cows.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that would be in the carriage and carrying the stuff back to the-- to the [INAUDIBLE], the places where the cows were housed, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can't think of the word in English right now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- so primarily with animals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Also loved riding horses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I always used to go there and the-- the keeper of the animals, his name was an old gentleman, [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Ilmi. ?] He was a vegetarian and he loved animals.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He absolutely kind of was my mentor because he knew how much I loved animals.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So there was a Arabian thoroughbred that was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
